Create a dummyplot

Descr of this plot

dummyplot(x, y, col)

Arguments

x

x coordinates
y

y coordinates
col

color of points

Value

ggplot object

Examples

library(random.cdisc.data)


ASL <- radam("ASL", start_with = list(WEIGHT = c(80, 85, 90), STUDYID = "A"))

with(ASL, dummyplot(WEIGHT, BAGE, ARM))

dummyplot(x = ASL$WEIGHT, y = ASL$BAGE, col = ASL$ARM)
